":"2019-09-01T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8byEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=d6ae4094\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8feff0d02fa74c6e01bfb1407419044acef32a1f","tid":1525790,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bae4005df87210bdadb3a45f1ed9d5e36bf0376","tid":1525790,"uid":142896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e29b15102bad9be75edc437480d3eeab9a08df0","tid":1525790,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"死link啊巴打<br />\n推！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdUrYHMwaGYgR9FOe-LOA4EXnEwZzyeMRuW5kZBUjPVcPUIZQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdUrYHMwaGYgR9FOe-LOA4EXnEwZzyeMRuW5kZBUjPVcPUIZQ%2Fviewform&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8byEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=f0d8feec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdUrYHMwaGYgR9FOe-LOA4EXnEwZzyeMRuW5kZBUjPVcPUIZQ/viewform</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"已填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議樓主開過個新post重推新link <br />\n<br />\n同埋可以加一條問題係畀人答自己做咩stream<br />\n<br />\n例如音樂/電影 行內咁多唔同profession<br />\n之後先分類會好麻煩"},{"pid":"e4aeeb9906246bc0550ea194ae6f7f2d117f373a","tid":1525790,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n從今以後香港精神長存<br />\n反共反泯滅人性政權之文化建邦！"},{"pid":"a022c7b6e293799f8caee1c6f85a6d387643e9cb","tid":1525790,"uid":302068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"support!"},{"pid":"ec81b0b50321f5adff08adab277567bfa670aa43","tid":1525790,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee26d01eaa3869c822e85c49135bced40651f92","tid":1525790,"uid":142896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:00:18.000Z","msg":"開呢個ｐｏｓｔ係想招募人一齊成立一個<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>宣揚香港文化同精神既娛樂文化團體</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日開始，我地要令全世界係學粵語而唔係普通話；學繁體字而唔係簡體字；學真正中國歷史同真正百家思想而唔係上虛偽既孔子學院。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要知道，保護我地民族，必須先保護我地自己既語言同文字，</span></strong></ins></span>先可以保護到自身既文化同民族精神。舉個例，猶太人。佢地即使經歷二千年既逼害同逃亡，至今「猶太人」一詞，仍然長存。猶太人就算身在何方，都一定會學習希伯來文，並嚴謹遵守猶太教既教條，所以，你見到猶太人點解仲可以保留共民族名字，正因佢地身上，猶太人既一切，都完整保留著。<br />\n再睇下港女最愛既韓國，韓國政府支助當地娛樂公司事業同藝術發展，唔講文藝果邊，剩係講韓星同k-pop，大家有目共賭，K-pop個youtube view數同多國music有得揮，多人因而學韓文，學韓式打扮，食韓國野。<br />\n回想我地有哥哥梅豔芬四大天王李小龍既年代，對亞洲甚至全球影響有幾大？同樣道理，可見「明星」同「音樂文化」係有幾大影響力，當你既民族／國家有一個具影響力既文化時，就會有世界既注目，留意你既一切同想學習你既文化，<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至你既政治</span></span></strong></ins>。<br />\n<br />\n同時，大家見到，感受到，呢十年來，本地音樂慢慢失去支持，香港人慢慢聽少左廣東歌，睇少左粵語劇，個個都娘娘上身宮廷劇上身，真正既中國文化歷史呢？我睇，以為唔會再有電視劇敢提。<br />\n唔多講，明既人其實呢一刻已經有共鳴，我係度誠邀各位，不論你係學生，做緊野；不論你係做拍劇定音樂定跳舞甚至時裝，非常歡迎你加入。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當然，金主都非常歡迎！</strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n「<span style=\"color: pink;\">我希望，以後來香港旅遊既係有文化同想學真正中國文化既遊客而唔係水貨客</span>」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">我希望，香港成為最後能堅守粵語既地方</span>」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: orange;\">我希望，比到世界睇到我地香港人既作品</span>」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: gold;\">我希望，香港可以成為一片中華文化既最後一片淨土</span>」<br />\n「<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我希望&hellip;&hellip;香港人呢三個字，永世長存</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>加入表格：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/wnjqx9N6UGJvp39c9 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fwnjqx9N6UGJvp39c9%20&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8byEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8b1c9e95\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/wnjqx9N6UGJvp39c9 </a> </ins></span><br />\n <br />\n<em><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">初步計劃</span></span></strong></ins></em><br />\n第一步：<br />\n支持本土音樂人，為佢地製作有水準既MV，希望可以有專業音樂人或者導師指導一下比如唱功，甚至有跳舞訓練，令到ＭＶ點擊率提升。<br />\n例子，我近日聽到好多為今次活動創作出來既歌，分享下比大家聽：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=imjZ7aHZRuY&amp;list=RDimjZ7aHZRuY&amp;start_radio=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DimjZ7aHZRuY%26list%3DRDimjZ7aHZRuY%26start_radio%3D1&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8byEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=4294e3b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=imjZ7aHZRuY&amp;list=RDimjZ7aHZRuY&amp;start_radio=1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Len-fvBvp4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLen-fvBvp4c&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8byEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=f6960195\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Len-fvBvp4c</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LxJ93vUsDjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLxJ93vUsDjw&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8byEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=23542f9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LxJ93vUsDjw</a><br />\n第二步：<br />\n微劇集，充滿正確價值觀，體現到真既中華文化或者本土精神既「偶像劇」<br />\n之後就睇下行成點<br />\n<br />\n最重要係！即使你唔係以上招募對象，<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>但你地對本地創作既支持係非常重要！</strong></span><br />\n點解咁多人鍾意去日本？日本文化氣息點解咁濃厚？正正因為日本人對自既文化有極大既尊重同支持。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家今日起，重捨你對本地創作既支持，<em><span style=\"color: red;\">令到「香港人」呢三個字，成為一種驕傲同自豪</span></em>。</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"新link<br />\n<br />\n(重開link已update)我希望「香港人」呢三個字永世長存<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1526308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1526308</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"789cf644dd0753f8ff51b8cd2c0d2f27226a557c","tid":1525790,"uid":255659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"Link invalid"},{"pid":"f3c4fdd5d56d8386b79c2bc3554dc79aada2fdd1","tid":1525790,"uid":293674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"d9ef6ac32843a7446052f2a388028b459ea17fc4","tid":1525790,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f5642fc65f12987932bf9e60979e28ac69bcf8","tid":1525790,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789cf644dd0753f8ff51b8cd2c0d2f27226a557c","tid":1525790,"uid":255659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"Link invalid"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:10:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdUrYHMwaGYgR9FOe-LOA4EXnEwZzyeMRuW5kZBUjPVcPUIZQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"h